    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In former Spanish colonies, for example in South and North America, wandering singers with a guitar who improvised songs. In current usage, popular singers who improvise songs accompanied by guitar.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
